name: Drinkadviser
0:
”Alexa, open drink suggestions”
”what should we drink?”
”what drink should i get?”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: drink suggestions
des: Ever had a party or wanted to bring alcohol to your friend, but never knew what kind of drink you should get? Well the answer is here just ask Alexa, what should I drink or What drink should I get, and Alexa will give you suggestions on what to drink tonight!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
